(D) Members of the commission who are members of the 48
general assembly shall serve terms on the commission concurrent 49
with their term in the general assembly. 50
(E) A member of the commission may be removed at the will 51
of the member's appointing authority. Vacancies shall be filled 52
in the same manner as original appointments. 53
(F) The affirmative vote of not fewer than four members of 54
the commission is required for any action of the commission. 55
(G) Members of the commission are not entitled to 56
